content:
Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Manage Your Intelligent Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, and Einstein Discovery.

Intelligent Analytics Apps provide curated paths through your data and powerful tools for deep explorations. With an intelligent app, you have a purpose-built set of analyses and insights about a specific area of your business.

Revenue Intelligence uses CRM Analytics, Einstein Forecasting, and other AI to deliver intelligent, data-driven insights in the context where sales teams work.

Service Intelligence determines whether you're meeting customer service goals with easy-to-understand data visualizations, using Data Cloud, CRM Analytics, and Einstein Conversation Mining.

Segment Intelligence combines Data Cloud and CRM Analytics to surface insights on segments across multiple channels, engagement types, and conversion sources.

Field Service Intelligence enhances customer engagement with real-time personalization, optimizes mobile workers with a best-in-class scheduling engine, and improves field visits with trusted AI built on the Einstein 1 Platform.

Commerce Intelligence natively connects commerce experiences to sales, service, and marketing apps, activating data from any source with ease.

Use the App Management tab to manage Intelligent Apps, monitor installs, view logs, update and delete apps, schedule app refreshes.
title: Salesforce Intelligent Analytics Apps
